---
title: Sausage Stuffed Chicken with Roast Potatoes, Broccoli and an Easy Pan Sauce
description: If you’re wondering about that lonely sausage in your box this week it’s destined for this awesome recipe! We asked our butcher Nick to put together some delicious sausages, to create a really easy stuffing for tonight’s chicken. With an easy pan sauce, this recipe is simple to make yet bound to impress
